Interface UserValidation

All Superinterfaces:
Function<User, ValidationResult>
public interface UserValidation extends Function<User, ValidationResult>
The UserValidation interface defines a rule for checking if a User is valid. It extends Function<User, ValidationResult> and includes methods to combine or create rules.
